## UPLOAD INSTRUCTIONS:

### 1. Upload .htaccess:
- Download `.htaccess-namecheap` from this project
- Rename to `.htaccess`
- Upload to `/public_html/` via cPanel File Manager
- Replace existing .htaccess file

### 2. Follow SSL Guide:
- Read `NAMECHEAP_SSL_GUIDE.md` 
- Find SSL options in cPanel Security section
- Enable AutoSSL or Let's Encrypt
- Wait 5-15 minutes for certificate installation

### 3. Test Results:
- Visit https://www.stargate.ci
- Check for green lock icon in browser
- Test https://stargate.ci (should work or redirect)
- Run SSL test at ssllabs.com

